---
layout: base.njk
title: "Amenities | Mona Shores Flats"
description: "See what's included: granite kitchens, in-unit laundry, fitness center, pickleball courts, dog run, playground, clubhouse and detached garages in Norton Shores, MI."
---

<section class="section" style="padding-top:clamp(110px,14vw,180px)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stack" data-reveal>
      <div class="eyebrow">What's Included</div>
      <h2>See exactly what you're getting.</h2>
      <p class="lead">A brand-new 2025 community — real photos of the finishes and spaces, not a checklist of buzzwords.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <!-- 1 -->
      <div class="split" data-reveal>
        <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/kitchen.jpg" alt="Granite island kitchen with stainless appliances"></div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="eyebrow">In Your Home</div>
          <h3 class="feature-h">Chef-ready kitchens</h3>
          <p class="lead">Granite countertops with island layouts, a full stainless-steel appliance package, and a dishwasher in every home.</p>
          <ul class="feature__list"><li>Granite + island</li><li>Stainless appliances</li><li>Dishwasher &amp; microwave</li></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 2 -->
      <div class="split split--flip" data-reveal>
        <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/living.jpg" alt="Light-filled open-concept living room"></div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="eyebrow">In Your Home</div>
          <h3 class="feature-h">Light, open living</h3>
          <p class="lead">High ceilings and an open-concept layout, with a private balcony or patio off the living area and LVT flooring underfoot.</p>
          <ul class="feature__list"><li>High ceilings</li><li>Private balcony or patio</li><li>Central A/C &amp; heat</li></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 3 -->
      <div class="split" data-reveal>
        <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/laundry.jpg" alt="Full-size in-unit washer and dryer"></div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="eyebrow">In Your Home</div>
          <h3 class="feature-h">Laundry in every home</h3>
          <p class="lead">A full-size washer and dryer in your unit — no shared machines, no laundromat, no quarters.</p>
          <ul class="feature__list"><li>Full-size W/D included</li><li>Generous closets</li><li>Extra storage</li></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 4 -->
      <div class="split split--flip" data-reveal>
        <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/gym.jpg" alt="On-site fitness center"></div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="eyebrow">The Community</div>
          <h3 class="feature-h">Fitness without the membership</h3>
          <p class="lead">An on-site fitness center with cardio, strength equipment and a Peloton — open daily and free for residents.</p>
          <ul class="feature__list"><li>Cardio &amp; strength</li><li>Peloton</li><li>Open daily · free</li></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 5 -->
      <div class="split" data-reveal>
        <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/building.jpg" alt="Mona Shores Flats grounds and exterior"></div>
        <div class="stack">
          <div class="eyebrow">The Community</div>
          <h3 class="feature-h">Room to get outside</h3>
          <p class="lead">Pickleball courts, an on-site dog run, a playground, and a resident clubhouse — all on landscaped grounds, with detached garages available to rent.</p>
          <ul class="feature__list"><li>Pickleball &amp; dog run</li><li>Playground &amp; clubhouse</li><li>Detached garages</li></ul>
          <div style="margin-top:6px"><a class="btn btn--accent" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Everything included -->
    <div class="amen-group">
      <div class="amen-group__head" data-reveal><h3>Everything included</h3></div>
      <ul class="checklist" data-reveal>
        {% for a in site.amenities %}<li>{{ a.name }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section cta">
  <div class="wrap stack center">
    <h2>Come see it in person.</h2>
    <p>{{ site.special }}</p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.urls.availability }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check Availability →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
